name: ResidenceAndAccommodationType
title: Residence and Accommodation Type
publisher: HL7 US Realm Program Management Steward
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: A value set of SNOMED-CT codes descending from "365508006" "Residence and accommodation
circumstances - finding" reflecting type of residence, status of accommodations, living situation and environment.),(Data Element Scope: element that is used to describe housing situation),(Inclusion Criteria: All descendants of 365508006),(Exclusion Criteria: )
